          <source>Control passes from the <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>if<ept id="p1">**</ept> statement to the next statement in the program unless one of the <bpt id="p2">*</bpt>statement<ept id="p2">*</ept>s contains a <bpt id="p3">[</bpt>break<ept id="p3">](../cpp/break-statement-cpp.md)</ept>, <bpt id="p4">[</bpt>continue<ept id="p4">](../cpp/continue-statement-cpp.md)</ept>, or <bpt id="p5">[</bpt>goto<ept id="p5">](../cpp/goto-statement-cpp.md)</ept>.</source>
